(264, 13, 28, '<p>Some nodes may have pre-set configurations to choose from. With this event a pre-set can be set for a zone/sub-zone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A node that receive and act on this event send CLASS1.INFORMATION,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Type=48 as a response event.</p>', 'Set Pre-set'),
